ia Manager</h1><nav class="d-inline-block" aria-label="breadcrumb"><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="index.html">Home</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="features/headless-cms">Features</a></li><li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Media Manager</li></ol></nav></div></div></div></section><section class="wrapper bg-light wrapper-border"><div class="container py-14 py-md-16"><div class="row gx-lg-8 gx-xl-12 gy-10 align-items-center"><div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 position-relative"><div class="shape bg-line aqua rounded-circle rellax w-17 h-17" style="top:-2rem;left:-.6rem" data-rellax-speed="1">&nbsp;</div><div class="shape bg-pale-red rounded-circle rellax w-17 h-17" style="bottom:-2rem;right:-.4rem" data-rellax-speed="1">&nbsp;</div><figure class="rounded mb-0"><img src="/images/features/media_manager.png"></figure></div><div class="col-lg-6"><h3 class="display-4 mb-4">Media Manager</h3><p class="mb-5">Browse your images just like your favourite CMS. Use our media manager to manager your image library. Integrated with the HTML editor your images are available and all URL paths match your original CMS template.&nbsp;</p><div class="row gy-3"><div class="col-xl-6"><ul class="icon-list bullet-bg bullet-soft-aqua mb-0"><li><span><i class="uil uil-check"></i></span><span>Browse, create thumbnails and resize images.</span></li><li class="mt-3"><span><i class="uil uil-check"></i></span><span>Image information including page list.</span></li></ul></div><div class="col-xl-6"><ul class="icon-list bullet-bg bullet-soft-aqua mb-0"><li><span><i class="uil uil-check"></i></span><span>4x responsive image sizes.</span></li><li class="mt-3"><span><i class="uil uil-check"></i></span><span>Static URL'S match the CMS originals.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="wrapper bg-light wrapper-border"><div class="container py-14 py-md-16"><div class="row gx-lg-8 gx-xl-12 gy-10 align-items-center"><div c